  "title": "Ergot - a Global Threat to Sorghum",
  "abstract": "The current status of ergot (Claviceps sorghi and C. africana) of sorghum is reviewed. The biology, epidemiology, control, host plant resistance and integrated management strategies of the disease are discussed.",
